Program: Letter from America by Alistair Cooke
Title: Texas A&amp;M University
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/b043xgcr
Last Broadcast Date: Sun 9 Dec 1984
Not your average university - the Texas A&M does things on a grander scale. This archive edition of Letter from America was recorded by one of two listeners, who between them taped and labelled over 650 Letter From America programmes from 1973 to 1989. It was restored by the BBC in 2014.